      <title>法国总统梅朗雄称脱欧联盟将花费 2000 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-melenchon-says-left-alliance-to-spend-200-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果法国左翼联盟提前赢得大选，该联盟计划在未来五年投入 2000 亿欧元（2140 亿美元）公共资金用于优先考虑的事项，以扭转总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的劳工和养老金改革并促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-melenchon-says-left-alliance-to-spend-200-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:26:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京罕见出访亚洲安全伙伴 获益匪浅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/putin-s-rare-trip-to-asian-security-partners-pays-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京的亚洲之行为他赢得了支持，使他能够继续对乌克兰发动残酷的战争，同时也令韩国等大国感到震惊，韩国目前正考虑向基辅提供可能改变战场形势的武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/putin-s-rare-trip-to-asian-security-partners-pays-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞政党在民意调查中赢得支持；马克龙支持率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/le-pen-s-party-gains-support-in-poll-macron-approval-drops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五公布的一项民意调查显示，在法国立法选举前，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟党的支持率正在上升。另一项调查显示，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的支持率正在下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/le-pen-s-party-gains-support-in-poll-macron-approval-drops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙支持率跌至历史低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/macron-approval-rating-falls-to-match-previous-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五的一项民意调查显示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的支持率下降了 6 个百分点，创下历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/macron-approval-rating-falls-to-match-previous-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:08:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马拉维喜剧演员迈克尔·乌西被任命为副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/malawian-comedian-named-as-vice-president-after-chilima-s-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马拉维任命迈克尔·比兹维克·乌西为新任副总统，此前其前任索洛斯·奇利马于上周在一次飞机失事中丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/malawian-comedian-named-as-vice-president-after-chilima-s-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车关税迫在眉睫，德国哈贝克前往北京进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/germany-s-habeck-heads-to-beijing-for-talks-as-evs-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国副总理罗伯特·哈贝克即将抵达北京，与世界第二大经济体的高层领导人进行会谈，其中欧洲即将对中国电动汽车征收关税是其主要议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/germany-s-habeck-heads-to-beijing-for-talks-as-evs-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾立法者无视总统意愿，投票扩大权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-lawmakers-vote-to-expand-their-powers-defying-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法者再次投票决定扩大传唤公职人员的权力，无视抗议者和总统赖清德的反对。预计赖清德将请求宪法法院审查这些修改并暂停实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-lawmakers-vote-to-expand-their-powers-defying-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜军队第三次越界 韩国鸣枪警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/south-korea-fires-warning-shots-after-third-border-breach-by-north-s-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜军队越过边界后撤退，韩国士兵开枪警告，这是本月在朝鲜半岛发生的第三起此类事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/south-korea-fires-warning-shots-after-third-border-breach-by-north-s-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 03:25:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多亚洲领导人希望加入金砖国家，习近平和普京获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，俄罗斯总统普京和中国国务院总理李强分别在东南亚结束会晤之际，金砖国家经济集团的这两个合作伙伴遇到了一个渴望加入该组织的地区，该组织被视为对冲西方主导的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 01:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克立法者加强控制 媒体独立性面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/media-independence-at-risk-as-slovak-cabinet-tightens-grip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克立法者批准了一项公共媒体改革，实际上将广播公司置于政府控制之下，此举遭到反对派和国际组织的批评，被认为破坏了新闻独立性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/media-independence-at-risk-as-slovak-cabinet-tightens-grip</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 19:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
